WEBVTT

00:00:30.010 --> 00:00:32.464
I signed a stack of papers,

00:00:32.488 --> 00:00:34.218
gathered my personal effects,

00:00:34.242 --> 00:00:36.059
and left to join my wife

00:00:36.083 --> 00:00:38.648
who was waiting for me
at a nearby restaurant,

00:00:38.672 --> 00:00:40.482
completely unaware.

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:43.668
Fast-forward several hours,

00:00:43.692 --> 00:00:45.732
we both got really silly drunk.

00:00:45.756 --> 00:00:48.527
(Laughter)

00:00:48.551 --> 00:00:53.106
So, 40 plus years of continuous employment

00:00:53.130 --> 00:00:55.566
for a variety of companies,
large and small,

00:00:55.590 --> 00:00:57.026
was over.

00:00:57.050 --> 00:01:00.047
I had a good a network,
a good reputation --